'''Ugustin Uryus''' (s [[Tutlayt Talatint|tlatinit]] ''Aurelius Aogustinos'', s [[Tafransist|tfransist]]: ''Saint Augustin'') iga yan ger iflsusfn imaziɣn imqqurn ɣ umaḍal. Ilul taman taɣast ɣ tɣrmt n [[Suq Ahras]] ɣ tmazirt n [[Dzayr]] ass n 13 nuwanbir 354, ittumḍal ɣ 28 ɣuct 430 ɣ tɣrmt n [[Ɛnnaba]] ɣ tmazirt n [[Dzayr]]. Ayt dars gan kullu [[Imaziɣen|imaziɣn]] mac ar ttinin blli babas iḍfr irumiyn nɣ (afriqi arumi), innas uhu (tafriqit s tidt). Ar ittara s [[tutlayt talatnit]] iga yan zɣ kkuẓ ixatarn n tmzgida taṛumit ɣ ussan nns imzwura. Anamk n ism n Agṛṛam Arumi (s tafransist: Saint Ugustin), agṛṛam umbrwas , agṛṛam jirum , agṛṛam grigwar amzwaru ,d 33 ṭalb n tmzgida tarumit. Ikatulikiyn ar skarn akttay n tamttant nns ku 28 ɣuct. Urtuduksiyn nttni ar skarn akttay ass n 15 yulyu.

